Evaluation / Demo Mode

The OptQuest library can be used in conjunction with Optuna (and other frameworks) 
in demo/evaluation mode without requiring a commercial license key. This mode is 
provided solely for testing, evaluation, and demonstration purposes. Any use in 
production environments, commercial deployments, or for generating results 
intended for business decision-making requires a valid commercial license key.
